<!DOCTYPE html>
<html lang="en">
<head>
<meta charset="utf-8">
<meta http-equiv="X-UA-Compatible" content="IE=edge">
<meta name="viewport" content="width=device-width, initial-scale=1">
<base href="/">
<title>Stripe Payment Admin</title>
<link rel="stylesheet" href="css/bootstrap.min.css">
<link rel="stylesheet" href="css/bootstrap-theme.min.css">
<link rel="stylesheet" href="css/application.css">
<link rel="stylesheet" href="css/login.css">
<script src="js/jquery-1.12.4.min.js"></script>
<script src="js/bootstrap.min.js"></script>
</head>
<body>
    <div class="container main">
        <div class="row header">
            <div class="col-md-6 col-md-offset-3">
                <div class="text-center">
                    <h1 class="boldi light-blue">Ipefix Payment Solution</h1>
                </div>
            </div>
        </div>
        <div class="row">
            <div class="col-md-6 border-right">
                <div class="pull-right content-left">
                    <h2 class="dark-blue boldi">Stripe Payment Admin</h2>
                    <p>Cette partie du site est réservée,<br>vous devez fournir un login pour y entrer.</p>
                    <form action="{{ path_for('login') }}" method="post">
                        <div class="form-group">
                            <input type="email" name="login" class="form-control" placeholder="E-mail" required>
                            <button type="submit" class="btn btn-default btn-sm btn-block">Login</button>
                        </div>
                    </form>
                </div>
            </div>
            <div class="col-md-6 border-left">
                <div class="pull-left content-right">
                    <div class="img-logo">
                        <img src="images/logo-ipefix.png" alt="ipefix-logo">
                    </div>
                </div>
            </div>
            <div class="col-md-4 col-md-offset-4">
                <div class="text-center copyr">&copy; Ipefix 2019</div>
            </div>
        </div>
    </div>
</body>
</html>